CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Commercial Bancgroup is a bank holding company headquartered in Harrogate, Tennessee, operating primarily through its wholly owned bank subsidiary, Commercial Bank, a Tennessee banking corporation organized in 1976. The Bank is a full-service community banking institution that offers traditional consumer and commercial products and services to serve businesses and individuals in select markets in Kentucky, North Carolina, and Tennessee.
